<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩- فَاسْتَفْتِهِمْ أَهُمْ أَشَدُّ خَلْقاً أَمْ مَنْ خَلَقْنا إِنَّا خَلَقْناهُمْ مِنْ طِينٍ لازِبٍ <span class="c2">(١١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بَلْ عَجِبْتَ وَيَسْخَرُونَ <span class="c2">(١٢)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَإِذا ذُكِّرُوا لا يَذْكُرُونَ <span class="c2">(١٣)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٠- نَحْنُ أَعْلَمُ بِما يَقُولُونَ وَما أَنْتَ عَلَيْهِمْ بِجَبَّارٍ فَذَكِّرْ بِالْقُرْآنِ مَنْ يَخافُ وَعِيدِ <span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١١- وَذَكِّرْ فَإِنَّ الذِّكْرى تَنْفَعُ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ <span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١٢- فَذَكِّرْ فَما أَنْتَ بِنِعْمَةِ رَبِّكَ بِكاهِنٍ وَلا مَجْنُونٍ <span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١٣- فَذَكِّرْ إِنْ نَفَعَتِ الذِّكْرى <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَنْ يَخْشى <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١٤- فَذَكِّرْ إِنَّما أَنْتَ مُذَكِّرٌ <span class="c2">(٢١)</span> <span class="c2">«٦»</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
